hotelDescription:
In an area with businesses and laid-back eateries, this no-frills hotel is a 17-minute walk from Jadcherla train station, 7 km from KCR Eco Urban Park and 19 km from the Pillalamarri Banyan Tree.
 Unassuming rooms with wood furnishings offer Wi-Fi and TVs, as well as en suite wet rooms.
 Parking is available, as is traditional or continental breakfast. There's a back-up generator on-site.
